UID:tamir-squad-demo-2026
DTSTART:20260312T110000Z
DTEND:20260312T120000Z
SUMMARY:Setting Up Your Personal Squad — Demo by Tamir Dresher
LOCATION:Microsoft Teams
DESCRIPTION:Tamir Dresher presents a live demo on how to structure your AI team with Squad.\n\nSession covers:\n- How to structure your AI team with Squad\n- Using GitHub issues for task management\n- The Ralph work monitoring loop\n- Skills, decisions, and team artifacts\n- Live demo of setting up a personal squad\n\nNote: Time shown is 13:00 IST (UTC+2) | Alternative: 14:00 IST
